      "content": "Alright, I've seen the preliminary data you're pulling. The numbers look pretty bad. It seems like the core management engine and the primary reasoning clusters are responsible for about 40% of the total energy draw and the highest latency spikes due to the constant cross-node verification. Based on the goal of maximizing efficiency, what are your recommendations for those specific units?",
